nodes.text: This cantina proprietor was the manager of a cantina in which Boba Fett gunned down a mark. Angered, the cantina proprietor yelled at Fett to take his mark and leave the premises. Fett gave the proprietor a hefty sum of money as a compensation and left the place.
While unnamed, this NPC is a participant in the event that initiates the scenario that he appears in.
